CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1956, pg. 26 reads: "Who Will Be "Miss WILY"? you pick the winner...Barbara M. Robinson, Pittsburgh, Announcement of the winner and the coronation of "Miss WILY" will take place at Warners Cinerama, 336 Fifth Ave., Tuesday Evening, November 27th."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Barbara M. Robinson wearing a light colored short sleeve shirt with dark embroidery around the collar, posed in interior with light colored wall and chairs for "Miss WILY" contest, another version
